cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference Deixis-Bench in an internal report, cite this file with the exact release tag."
title: "Deixis-Bench: Situated Reference Resolution Under Visual Context Shift"
abstract: "Internal benchmark for the visual-context selection decision in a wearable live-assistant camera product. Scores the prior-vs-current visual-context anchor on a frozen scenario set under three intervention conditions; primary score is balanced Turn 2 accuracy under the baseline ranking condition."
